WEBVTT

01:53.020 --> 01:53.740
Hello, Mingying.

01:53.740 --> 01:54.539
Check Weibo.

01:55.539 --> 01:56.580
Cen Sisi committed suicide.

01:56.580 --> 01:57.500
Many netizens are guessing

01:57.500 --> 01:58.380
that you forced her to do so.

02:02.979 --> 02:03.500
What happened?

02:03.580 --> 02:05.339
By the time you read this,

02:05.699 --> 02:06.419
I will be in a place

02:06.419 --> 02:07.539
without pain.

02:07.619 --> 02:08.660
Goodbye, my love.

02:08.660 --> 02:09.459
Cen Sisi

02:09.459 --> 02:10.220
and my love.

02:10.780 --> 02:11.380
committed suicide.

02:17.419 --> 02:18.699
[Don't be impulsive. Calm down.]

02:18.699 --> 02:19.259
[There are]

02:19.259 --> 02:20.139
[many beautiful things in life.]

02:20.139 --> 02:21.220
[Think about the people who love you.]

02:21.220 --> 02:22.139
[Don't do anything stupid.]

02:23.220 --> 02:24.060
Murderer.

02:24.500 --> 02:25.100
Do you know

02:25.100 --> 02:25.780
what you've done?

02:26.180 --> 02:27.259
You are a murderer.

02:30.620 --> 02:31.060
Hello?

02:31.579 --> 02:32.180
[Hello,]

02:32.579 --> 02:33.460
Are you Wen Xiang?

02:34.539 --> 02:35.299
Are you the one

02:35.299 --> 02:36.500
who caused Su Cheng's suicide?

02:37.139 --> 02:38.060
Do you have anything to say?

02:39.620 --> 02:40.500
It's about Su Cheng.

02:43.859 --> 02:44.699
Or I'll come to you

02:44.699 --> 02:45.380
for a talk.

02:47.979 --> 02:49.100
Your information has been leaked.

02:49.419 --> 02:50.539
Don't answer unknown calls.

02:51.220 --> 02:52.180
I'll go back to the firm now

02:52.180 --> 02:53.259
to prepare an emergency plan.

02:53.419 --> 02:54.460
Let's keep in touch.

02:54.579 --> 02:54.940
Okay.

02:57.900 --> 02:58.539
Let's go.

03:00.699 --> 03:01.579
What should we do now?

03:01.900 --> 03:02.780
We don't know

03:02.780 --> 03:03.500
what's going on with Cen Sisi.

03:04.299 --> 03:05.019
Don't worry.

03:05.299 --> 03:06.259
Let's see if we can contact

03:06.259 --> 03:07.259
Cen Sisi's family.

03:07.579 --> 03:08.380
Think about it.

03:12.460 --> 03:13.100
Li Shican.

03:13.780 --> 03:15.100
Li Shican should be able to...

03:19.579 --> 03:21.019
Shican, Cen Sisi...

03:21.220 --> 03:21.739
I see.

03:22.340 --> 03:23.259
I've contacted her father.

03:23.900 --> 03:24.699
If all goes well,

03:24.819 --> 03:25.380
she should have been

03:25.380 --> 03:26.579
taken to the Municipal People's Hospital.

03:28.340 --> 03:28.900
How did she...

03:29.299 --> 03:29.900
She took some pills.

03:30.660 --> 03:31.539
But she was sent to the hospital in time.

03:32.100 --> 03:32.699
Don't worry.

03:32.819 --> 03:33.460
I'll go check on her first.

03:33.780 --> 03:34.299
Okay.

03:36.299 --> 03:37.620
He said Cen Sisi

03:37.699 --> 03:38.940
has been taken to the Municipal People's Hospital.

03:39.100 --> 03:40.060
He's already on his way there.

03:40.380 --> 03:41.259
What should we do now?

03:41.620 --> 03:42.380
Let's head to the hospital first.

03:42.620 --> 03:43.579
It's important to get the results

03:43.579 --> 03:44.139
as soon as possible.

03:44.180 --> 03:44.660
Get in the car.

03:45.299 --> 03:45.780
Okay.

03:47.620 --> 03:48.139
Thank you.

04:02.940 --> 04:03.419
Baby,

04:03.419 --> 04:04.419
I brought you some Xiaolongbao.

04:06.699 --> 04:07.220
What's going on?

04:08.539 --> 04:09.859
She's not picking up.

04:10.100 --> 04:10.979
Something happened to Ruan Yu.

04:10.979 --> 04:11.780
I'm going out.

04:12.419 --> 04:13.380
I'll go with you.

04:13.380 --> 04:13.780
No need.

04:14.380 --> 04:15.500
You didn't sleep last night.

04:15.500 --> 04:16.259
You should get some rest.

04:16.419 --> 04:17.180
I can handle it myself.

04:18.699 --> 04:19.139
Alright.

04:21.340 --> 04:22.259
Where's your ring?

04:24.340 --> 04:25.260
With the recent live streaming,

04:25.419 --> 04:26.619
there are a lot of staff around.

04:26.739 --> 04:27.660
I'm afraid of losing it,

04:27.660 --> 04:28.340
so I put it away.

04:28.580 --> 04:29.660
Okay, I'm leaving.

04:30.739 --> 04:31.539
Be careful.

04:31.700 --> 04:32.179
Bye.

04:44.660 --> 04:45.499
Please answer.

04:45.739 --> 04:46.539
How is she?

04:46.539 --> 04:47.340
What's the situation now?

04:47.780 --> 04:48.619
Is she out of danger?

04:53.780 --> 04:54.340
Look over here.

04:54.539 --> 04:55.660
There's a follow-up camera. Take another route.

04:56.140 --> 04:56.539
Hurry up.

04:56.539 --> 04:57.460
Please answer our question.

04:58.460 --> 04:58.979
This way.

05:00.140 --> 05:00.539
Come on.

05:11.299 --> 05:11.979
Say something.

05:11.979 --> 05:12.820
Be quiet, please.

05:12.820 --> 05:13.539
Be quiet.

05:14.340 --> 05:15.460
This is a hospital.

05:16.059 --> 05:17.299
The patient needs rest.

05:17.299 --> 05:18.460
Don't crowd around and keep quiet.

05:18.460 --> 05:18.979
Okay?

05:23.059 --> 05:23.580
Go.

05:29.100 --> 05:29.700
Look.

05:29.939 --> 05:30.780
Is that Wen Xiang?

05:31.379 --> 05:32.020
Guys,

05:40.179 --> 05:40.979
Li Shican!

05:40.979 --> 05:42.220
It's Li Shican!

05:42.220 --> 05:43.499
Come on!

05:45.979 --> 05:46.580
Guys,

05:46.660 --> 05:47.820
please keep order.

05:48.220 --> 05:49.260
If you have any questions,

05:49.299 --> 05:50.619
follow me, I'll answer them.

05:51.220 --> 05:52.020
Okay.

05:53.140 --> 05:54.460
Let's go.

05:59.939 --> 06:01.220
Not here, let's go.

06:02.619 --> 06:03.939
He's trying to control the narrative.

06:04.460 --> 06:05.299
Regardless of whether

06:05.299 --> 06:06.299
Cen Sisi is rescued,

06:06.700 --> 06:07.379
I'll likely be

06:07.379 --> 06:08.460
blamed as the perpetrator.

06:09.739 --> 06:10.419
He's trying to

06:10.419 --> 06:11.619
bring up his relationship with Cen Sisi

06:12.460 --> 06:13.460
to shift public attention

06:13.460 --> 06:14.460
onto himself.

06:16.179 --> 06:17.660
A celebrity's discussion

06:17.900 --> 06:18.900
will indeed generate more attention.

06:19.299 --> 06:20.340
You said you're friends with Su Cheng.

06:20.340 --> 06:21.299
what exactly was your relationship?

06:21.499 --> 06:22.499
How close were you?

06:22.780 --> 06:23.580
Was she your girlfriend?

06:23.900 --> 06:24.900
Or your ex-girlfriend?

06:25.979 --> 06:27.299
We were never together,

06:27.499 --> 06:28.660
and there was never any ambiguity.

06:29.140 --> 06:30.660
So what were her feelings for you?

06:30.820 --> 06:31.460
Do you know?

06:35.820 --> 06:36.939
So you're saying

06:36.939 --> 06:38.100
she committed suicide because she didn't get

06:38.100 --> 06:39.179
the emotional support she needed from you?

06:39.260 --> 06:40.100
Is that true?

06:40.979 --> 06:42.020
Regardless of

06:42.140 --> 06:43.739
the final outcome,

06:44.660 --> 06:45.900
Su Cheng's emotional instability

06:46.379 --> 06:47.379
is rooted in me.

06:47.900 --> 06:48.539
What role

06:48.539 --> 06:49.859
does Wen Xiang play

06:49.859 --> 06:50.900
in your relationship?

06:52.499 --> 06:53.619
Don't drag unrelated people

06:53.820 --> 06:54.900
into this.

06:57.260 --> 06:57.820
Where are you going?

06:58.539 --> 06:59.780
I can't let him ruin his future.

07:00.299 --> 07:01.179
Cen Sisi,

07:01.179 --> 07:01.700
I'm innocent.

07:01.700 --> 07:02.739
I have nothing to fear.

07:03.020 --> 07:03.700
The law will clear

07:03.700 --> 07:04.700
my name.

07:05.020 --> 07:05.499
But if Li Shican

07:05.499 --> 07:06.179
gets involved now,

07:06.179 --> 07:07.419
he'll be tainted.

07:07.660 --> 07:08.700
He's an adult.

07:08.939 --> 07:09.900
He can

07:09.900 --> 07:11.379
take responsibility for his actions.

07:12.020 --> 07:13.460
He's already made a public statement.

07:13.619 --> 07:14.619
Going there now

07:14.820 --> 07:16.260
will only make things more complicated.

07:21.179 --> 07:21.739
I'm sorry.

07:23.660 --> 07:24.179
It's okay.

07:29.539 --> 07:30.739
Cen Sisi is out of danger.

07:30.939 --> 07:32.179
The paparazzi have been driven out of the hospital.

07:32.419 --> 07:33.140
Where are you?

07:33.379 --> 07:34.100
I'll come to you.

07:35.939 --> 07:36.619
Li Shican said

07:36.619 --> 07:37.539
he's coming to see me now.

07:44.260 --> 07:45.379
Tell him we're on B2.

07:46.220 --> 07:47.900
License plate number B6H8.

07:47.939 --> 07:48.820
B6H8.

07:49.100 --> 07:49.859
Tell his assistant

07:49.859 --> 07:51.580
to drive the nanny car out first.

07:52.179 --> 07:52.979
Let him

07:53.260 --> 07:54.739
take the safety passage to the ward.

08:09.780 --> 08:10.419
He's coming.

08:27.020 --> 08:27.660
Don't worry.

08:27.939 --> 08:28.939
She's been saved.

08:29.379 --> 08:30.059
Everything

08:30.299 --> 08:31.140
will be fine.

08:31.499 --> 08:32.260
What about you?

08:32.979 --> 08:33.739
I...

08:35.419 --> 08:36.220
It's just public opinion.

08:37.299 --> 08:38.100
It will pass.

08:40.300 --> 08:42.220
By the way, I just found out

08:42.580 --> 08:43.739
that the online exposure

08:43.859 --> 08:44.659
of Cen Sisi's

08:44.659 --> 08:45.779
real information

08:46.220 --> 08:47.139
was staged by her.

08:49.019 --> 08:49.859
She's trying to

08:49.859 --> 08:50.940
create the image of a victim

08:51.180 --> 08:52.340
and build up public opinion

08:52.859 --> 08:55.220
to make a scene on the day of the trial.

08:58.659 --> 08:59.859
She really cares about me.

09:01.659 --> 09:02.300
It's okay.

09:02.820 --> 09:04.060
It's just a minor issue.

09:04.779 --> 09:05.180
You should

09:05.379 --> 09:06.619
get some rest early,

09:07.180 --> 09:08.180
and avoid checking Weibo for a while.

09:14.139 --> 09:15.019
I'll take her back.

09:15.739 --> 09:16.340
You...

09:20.220 --> 09:20.779
Lawyer Xu,

09:21.100 --> 09:22.060
could you please

09:22.060 --> 09:22.979
escort me out?

09:23.420 --> 09:24.019
My assistant

09:24.019 --> 09:25.460
has been sent away by you.

09:25.700 --> 09:28.300
This hospital is a sensitive area.

09:28.659 --> 09:29.540
It's not convenient for me

09:29.739 --> 09:30.379
to go out alone.

09:36.180 --> 09:36.779
Lawyer Xu,

09:38.779 --> 09:39.619
thank you.

09:42.979 --> 09:43.499
Seat belt.

09:52.619 --> 09:53.060
Kelly.

09:53.540 --> 09:53.979
Attorney Liu,

09:54.859 --> 09:56.340
if anyone calls to ask

09:56.619 --> 09:57.300
about Miss Ruan Yu,

09:58.019 --> 09:58.739
don't respond.

09:58.979 --> 09:59.379
Okay.

09:59.619 --> 10:00.019
Okay.

10:00.420 --> 10:01.259
I'm at the law firm.

10:01.899 --> 10:02.700
Selling liquor

10:02.700 --> 10:03.300
isn't that easy.

10:03.300 --> 10:04.460
You need to find the right clientele

10:04.460 --> 10:05.619
and make them willingly buy.

10:05.619 --> 10:06.100
Got it?

10:06.619 --> 10:07.700
Alright, I'm hanging up.

10:08.220 --> 10:09.300
-Find the right clientele. -Hello.

10:09.300 --> 10:10.180
You've come to the law firm.

10:11.779 --> 10:12.580
Are you talking to me?

10:14.139 --> 10:14.940
Sorry,

10:15.420 --> 10:16.259
we don't buy liquor here.

10:16.540 --> 10:17.619
Do I look like a salesman?

10:19.180 --> 10:20.700
Then, do you come here

10:20.700 --> 10:21.700
to hire a lawyer?

10:21.940 --> 10:22.700
No, I'm here to...

10:22.700 --> 10:23.220
If you don't hire a lawyer,

10:23.220 --> 10:24.019
why are you here?

10:27.979 --> 10:28.540
I've seen

10:28.540 --> 10:29.659
many salesmen

10:30.019 --> 10:30.779
like you.

10:31.820 --> 10:32.979
Leave here now.

10:33.379 --> 10:34.580
Don't make me force you to leave.

10:35.940 --> 10:36.739
What do you want?

10:38.379 --> 10:39.100
Have you ever eaten tofu?

10:39.700 --> 10:40.619
Tofu has brains,

10:40.619 --> 10:41.540
but you don't have any.

10:41.820 --> 10:42.540
Why are you so sensitive?

10:42.659 --> 10:43.739
You've been scammed by a bar hostess, right?

10:43.739 --> 10:44.859
Scammed for money or for sex?

10:44.859 --> 10:45.139
The kind that gets sold

10:45.139 --> 10:46.220
and counts money for others, right?

10:46.779 --> 10:47.739
Who are you calling a tofu brain?

10:47.739 --> 10:48.420
I'm talking about you.

10:48.979 --> 10:49.580
I'm telling you,

10:49.940 --> 10:50.739
I don't have time today.

10:50.739 --> 10:51.220
or I would

10:51.220 --> 10:52.180
have a good talk with you.

10:53.340 --> 10:54.460
Am I right?

10:55.259 --> 10:55.659
Hello,

10:56.340 --> 10:56.979
I want to ask

10:56.979 --> 10:57.899
if Lawyer Xu Huaisong is here.

10:58.820 --> 10:59.899
He's not here today.

11:01.139 --> 11:02.220
How do you know Xu Huaisong?

11:02.300 --> 11:03.619
It's none of your business.

11:03.940 --> 11:05.100
What about Lawyer Liu Mao?

11:06.180 --> 11:07.180
How do you know me?

11:07.180 --> 11:08.379
Who are you?

11:09.420 --> 11:09.899
Liu Mao?

11:10.700 --> 11:11.259
I...

11:13.100 --> 11:13.619
You...

11:14.619 --> 11:15.259
Which Liu Mao?

11:16.139 --> 11:17.019
Which Liu Mao are you looking for?

11:18.100 --> 11:19.220
There's only one Liu Mao in this firm.

11:19.340 --> 11:19.979
That's me.

11:20.060 --> 11:21.060
The one who went on a blind date with Ruan Yu.

11:21.139 --> 11:21.899
Wait, who are you?

11:21.899 --> 11:23.019
How do you know Ruan Yu?

11:23.139 --> 11:24.220
I'm Ruan Yu's...

11:25.379 --> 11:25.859
Bestie.

11:29.979 --> 11:30.499
Bestie.

11:31.139 --> 11:31.859
Bestie.

11:43.700 --> 11:44.300
Hello, hello.

11:44.300 --> 11:45.340
Hello, hello, bestie.

11:45.340 --> 11:45.779
Nice to meet you.

11:45.779 --> 11:46.540
Nice to meet you.

11:46.899 --> 11:47.540
Sorry, sorry.

11:47.540 --> 11:47.979
I...

11:49.019 --> 11:50.379
I didn't mean to...

11:50.379 --> 11:51.139
I didn't mean to stop you.

11:51.139 --> 11:51.659
I didn't mean to...

11:51.659 --> 11:52.499
I didn't mean to either.

11:52.499 --> 11:54.139
I didn't expect you to be

11:54.460 --> 11:55.820
so pure and kind.

11:56.499 --> 11:57.580
I didn't expect

11:57.619 --> 12:00.340
my bestie to be so open-minded.

12:05.259 --> 12:05.940
What can I do for you?

12:07.139 --> 12:07.820
I'm looking for Ruan Yu.

12:07.820 --> 12:08.700
She's missing.

12:10.259 --> 12:11.259
She went to the hospital

12:11.420 --> 12:12.659
with Xu Huaisong to see Cen Sisi.

12:13.340 --> 12:14.700
You let her go to the hospital?

12:14.779 --> 12:16.139
But the hospital has reporters.

12:16.139 --> 12:17.499
What if she's in danger?

12:18.100 --> 12:18.859
Calm down.

12:19.139 --> 12:19.940
We've already

12:19.940 --> 12:20.659
controlled the public opinion.

12:21.100 --> 12:21.940
And she's with Xu Huaisong.

12:21.940 --> 12:22.540
They're together.

12:22.540 --> 12:23.619
What danger could there possibly be?

12:25.300 --> 12:25.779
Tell me,

12:25.779 --> 12:27.100
how can I reach Ruan Yu now?

12:30.540 --> 12:31.499
If you don't mind,

12:32.019 --> 12:33.139
add me on WeChat.

12:33.940 --> 12:36.259
I'll keep you updated.

12:38.700 --> 12:39.100
Fine.

12:39.580 --> 12:40.019
Fine,

12:44.220 --> 12:45.619
but let me be clear.

12:45.619 --> 12:46.580
If you can't handle

12:46.580 --> 12:47.060
this right,

12:47.540 --> 12:49.100
or can't protect my Ruan Yu,

12:49.420 --> 12:50.379
I'll come back and I'll...

12:51.220 --> 12:52.139
Liu You Yu,

12:52.499 --> 12:53.659
I won't be so forgiving.

12:55.820 --> 12:56.580
Alright, alright.

12:56.779 --> 12:57.499
If anything happens,

12:57.499 --> 12:58.420
I'll keep you updated.

12:59.019 --> 12:59.420
Fine.

13:00.259 --> 13:01.619
Thank you.

13:02.180 --> 13:02.580
You're welcome.

13:03.300 --> 13:03.820
Take care.

13:05.979 --> 13:06.940
Take care, Miss.

13:08.700 --> 13:09.340
Blossom and Wealth.

13:14.220 --> 13:15.540
Don't tell anyone about this.

13:19.420 --> 13:21.340
Your name doesn't match your appearance.

13:21.340 --> 13:22.340
You should change your name.

13:32.420 --> 13:33.379
Uncle Cen.

13:37.779 --> 13:38.820
Cen Sisi's father.

13:54.100 --> 13:55.220
Is this Miss Ruan?

13:59.700 --> 14:01.100
I'm Sisi's father.

14:01.420 --> 14:01.979
I'd like

14:02.300 --> 14:03.700
to talk to you about Sisi.

14:06.820 --> 14:07.220
Hello,

14:07.499 --> 14:08.220
if you have any issues,

14:08.220 --> 14:09.220
you can talk to me directly.

14:09.460 --> 14:10.779
I'm Miss Ruan's lawyer.

14:25.300 --> 14:26.180
I'm sorry, Miss Ruan,

14:27.220 --> 14:28.420
for causing you any trouble.

14:29.060 --> 14:31.379
I apologize on behalf of Sisi.

14:32.180 --> 14:33.499
As her father,

14:34.420 --> 14:36.220
I also want to apologize.

14:37.300 --> 14:38.300
I've been negligent

14:38.619 --> 14:40.540
to her,

14:41.259 --> 14:42.100
which led to

14:43.060 --> 14:44.420
this situation.

14:50.619 --> 14:51.259
Miss Ruan,

14:52.180 --> 14:53.300
could we talk

14:53.859 --> 14:54.859
in private?

15:13.460 --> 15:14.420
I just received

15:14.739 --> 15:16.460
Sisi's diagnosis report today.

15:16.739 --> 15:17.340
It confirms

15:17.859 --> 15:19.580
that she has a serious mental illness.

15:20.259 --> 15:21.379
She has shown

15:21.979 --> 15:22.499
some paranoid

15:22.499 --> 15:23.659
in her daily life,

15:24.100 --> 15:24.979
not just against you.

15:28.019 --> 15:28.540
Of course,

15:29.300 --> 15:30.060
I'm not saying this

15:30.899 --> 15:31.940
to win

15:32.180 --> 15:34.019
your sympathy

15:34.019 --> 15:34.739
or understanding.

15:35.499 --> 15:36.379
I just think

15:36.859 --> 15:37.659
you deserve

15:37.659 --> 15:38.499
an explanation.

15:41.659 --> 15:42.379
Thank you.

15:45.340 --> 15:47.139
I'm aware of your demands

15:47.139 --> 15:48.100
and compensation demands,

15:48.499 --> 15:49.580
I've got them all.

15:50.379 --> 15:51.139
Besides,

15:51.700 --> 15:52.899
I want to compensate you

15:52.899 --> 15:53.899
for emotional distress.

15:54.220 --> 15:56.580
Or you can tell me

15:57.139 --> 15:58.379
what else you need.

16:04.180 --> 16:04.979
I just hope

16:05.700 --> 16:06.940
to minimize the impact

16:06.940 --> 16:07.700
of this incident.

16:08.460 --> 16:09.859
I want Li Shican and I

16:10.180 --> 16:11.300
to get back to normal as soon as possible.

16:15.940 --> 16:16.779
Of course.

16:25.979 --> 16:28.019
Lawyer Xu, thank you.

16:37.619 --> 16:39.340
Look, the leaves are turning yellow.

16:39.739 --> 16:42.340
Why does she still call you Lawyer Xu?

16:42.779 --> 16:44.300
Don't you know the character in her novel

16:44.300 --> 16:45.379
is you?

16:45.940 --> 16:46.619
Or

16:47.899 --> 16:48.659
you dare not admit it?

16:54.619 --> 16:56.300
You have a close relationship with Cen Sisi.

16:57.619 --> 16:58.899
The real reason

16:58.899 --> 16:59.659
for her suicide

16:59.820 --> 17:00.619
is

17:00.779 --> 17:02.180
with Ruan Yu

17:02.700 --> 17:04.340
or you?

17:21.139 --> 17:21.619
Sir,

17:27.619 --> 17:29.459
you're also stubborn.

17:30.340 --> 17:31.179
You shouldn't

17:31.540 --> 17:32.459
have dealt with

17:32.459 --> 17:33.340
this matter today.

17:34.060 --> 17:35.060
I promise you,

17:35.619 --> 17:36.619
I'll cooperate with Shi Can

17:37.020 --> 17:38.500
to clarify all the facts.

17:39.100 --> 17:39.859
If necessary,

17:41.300 --> 17:42.820
I'll also disclose Sisi's condition.

17:46.939 --> 17:47.939
But I'm curious,

17:48.060 --> 17:49.379
how did you

17:50.419 --> 17:51.139
find your way

17:51.500 --> 17:52.580
here tonight?

17:54.780 --> 17:55.659
Oh, I almost forgot

17:56.139 --> 17:57.340
the most important thing.

17:58.100 --> 17:58.780
Miss Ruan,

17:59.899 --> 18:00.740
I found your address

18:01.219 --> 18:02.780
in Sisi's

18:03.020 --> 18:03.580
notebook.

18:04.100 --> 18:06.179
I'm not sure if she had

18:06.500 --> 18:07.780
any other extreme behaviors.

18:08.139 --> 18:09.219
For your safety,

18:09.820 --> 18:10.379
I hope

18:10.580 --> 18:11.699
you can move out for a while.

18:12.419 --> 18:13.980
I'm willing to cover

18:14.699 --> 18:15.780
any expenses that arise.

18:27.100 --> 18:27.459
Here.

18:28.459 --> 18:28.980
Thank you.

18:32.300 --> 18:32.820
Thank you.

18:38.899 --> 18:40.300
Why don't you pack some essentials

18:40.300 --> 18:41.020
and stay at my place?

18:41.500 --> 18:42.980
I've been away from home

18:42.980 --> 18:43.699
for the past month.

18:44.060 --> 18:45.179
And the security is good.

18:45.619 --> 18:46.300
No one can get in.

18:46.699 --> 18:47.459
Don't bother.

18:47.939 --> 18:49.020
I'll stay at Mingying's.

18:49.540 --> 18:50.899
She's close to you,

18:51.260 --> 18:52.780
and she's your editor.

18:53.500 --> 18:55.179
I don't think it's safe.

18:56.500 --> 18:57.060
Then...

18:58.540 --> 18:59.379
I'll go to my parents' house.

19:00.139 --> 19:00.939
Your personal information

19:00.939 --> 19:01.659
has been leaked too much.

19:01.899 --> 19:03.260
Parents are the same as friends.

19:06.699 --> 19:07.459
That's true.

19:08.020 --> 19:09.500
So come with me.

19:10.379 --> 19:10.859
No.

19:11.379 --> 19:12.699
You just showed up in front of the media

19:12.699 --> 19:13.219
today.

19:13.580 --> 19:15.020
It's easier to be targeted at your place.

19:17.859 --> 19:19.060
I'd better stay at a hotel.

19:20.260 --> 19:21.060
Forget about the hotel.

19:21.500 --> 19:22.419
According to my experience,

19:22.580 --> 19:23.899
if someone wants to dig into you,

19:24.060 --> 19:24.899
no matter what hotel you stay in,

19:24.980 --> 19:25.820
you can be dug out.

19:27.300 --> 19:27.699
Then...

19:30.340 --> 19:31.179
Then go to my place.

19:32.980 --> 19:33.659
I have an apartment

19:33.659 --> 19:34.419
near here.

19:35.100 --> 19:36.179
It's safe.

19:38.659 --> 19:40.780
Your apartment?

19:41.699 --> 19:42.219
Yes.

20:02.859 --> 20:03.340
Hello.

20:03.820 --> 20:05.580
Bro, Cen Sisi is awake.

20:06.219 --> 20:06.780
I see.

20:27.100 --> 20:28.139
Lawyer Liu told me

20:28.139 --> 20:29.260
Cen Sisi is fine, right?

20:29.419 --> 20:31.179
Yeah, luckily she's fine.

20:32.300 --> 20:33.379
Thank god.

20:34.060 --> 20:35.060
Have you been home?

20:35.379 --> 20:36.459
It might not be safe there.

20:36.619 --> 20:37.580
I haven't gone back. Come in.

20:38.419 --> 20:39.179
Where are you?

20:43.780 --> 20:44.780
Are you in a hotel?

20:45.020 --> 20:46.060
Are you safe alone?

20:46.060 --> 20:47.139
Should I come over now?

20:47.899 --> 20:48.340
Well,

20:49.980 --> 20:51.060
I'd rather...

20:52.260 --> 20:53.379
I've been driving all night.

20:55.340 --> 20:56.260
A man.

20:57.300 --> 20:59.100
Ruan Yu, you've got balls.

20:59.100 --> 20:59.939
Keep it down.

21:00.699 --> 21:01.540
It's not what you think.

21:01.980 --> 21:02.419
No.

21:02.619 --> 21:03.740
I wish it's what I think.

21:04.699 --> 21:05.580
Is it Xu Huaisong?

21:05.580 --> 21:06.540
Is he staying with you tonight?

21:07.419 --> 21:07.899
Alright, alright.

21:07.899 --> 21:08.820
I'll tell you later.

21:08.820 --> 21:09.260
Gotta go.

21:13.379 --> 21:14.379
Lawyer Xu.

21:15.419 --> 21:15.780
I...

21:16.379 --> 21:17.619
I'll go to the hotel across the street.

21:18.100 --> 21:19.899
It's safer for you.

21:20.780 --> 21:21.659
I'm sorry to bother you.

21:21.780 --> 21:22.219
It's okay.

21:22.379 --> 21:23.219
I've already booked the room.

21:23.459 --> 21:23.980
Have some water.

21:24.659 --> 21:25.260
Thank you.

21:27.020 --> 21:27.659
Sit on the sofa.

21:35.659 --> 21:36.179
Let's eat.

21:38.659 --> 21:39.219
You...

21:39.820 --> 21:40.580
Lawyer Xu,

21:41.139 --> 21:42.260
You brought the cat here.

21:44.100 --> 21:45.899
Isn't it hard to transport a cat across borders?

21:46.260 --> 21:48.060
Not really. There are transfer companies.

21:48.219 --> 21:48.980
It's quite convenient.

21:51.179 --> 21:51.980
Mimi

21:53.419 --> 21:54.219
has been tired all day.

21:54.899 --> 21:55.540
Take a rest.

21:55.699 --> 21:56.500
I'll go cook dinner.

21:58.859 --> 21:59.780
Thank you.

22:40.659 --> 22:41.260
Are you feeling better?

22:46.219 --> 22:46.980
Xiaofei said

22:46.980 --> 22:48.419
you went out to handle things.

22:50.219 --> 22:51.540
Who are you dealing with?

22:53.740 --> 22:54.540
Is it Ruan Yu?

22:58.260 --> 23:00.060
I was in the emergency room.

23:01.780 --> 23:03.100
But she's just scolded.

23:03.100 --> 23:04.139
She deserves your concern

23:05.100 --> 23:06.060
and your guilt.

23:10.540 --> 23:11.139
Sisi.

23:12.020 --> 23:13.300
No one in this world

23:13.500 --> 23:14.540
deserves you to hurt yourself.

23:14.820 --> 23:15.659
To punish the other person.

23:15.980 --> 23:16.980
But it works.

23:18.379 --> 23:19.500
When I was a child,

23:21.939 --> 23:23.300
it was just me and my nanny

23:24.100 --> 23:25.459
at home.

23:27.379 --> 23:29.300
The only way to get my dad's attention

23:30.820 --> 23:32.179
was to make myself sick.

23:33.939 --> 23:35.300
Only when I got a cold

23:36.780 --> 23:37.820
would he come home

23:37.820 --> 23:39.219
and hold my hand,

23:39.740 --> 23:41.139
saying he shouldn't have been

23:43.379 --> 23:44.980
so focused on work.

23:51.619 --> 23:53.100
Isn't that what you're doing now?

23:57.139 --> 23:58.340
How long has it been

23:59.659 --> 24:00.540
since you've really

24:00.540 --> 24:02.020
like this?

24:02.939 --> 24:04.699
Back in high school, you said

24:06.340 --> 24:08.020
if I couldn't find someone to talk to

24:08.340 --> 24:10.100
in Suzhou,

24:11.619 --> 24:13.500
I could share my life and thoughts

24:13.859 --> 24:15.859
with you, right?

24:16.139 --> 24:18.659
Sisi, as a friend,

24:18.939 --> 24:20.179
I'm willing to listen to you.

24:21.379 --> 24:22.179
But I can't

24:22.179 --> 24:23.340
always respond to you.

24:24.020 --> 24:25.100
I have my work,

24:25.500 --> 24:26.379
my life,

24:26.580 --> 24:27.820
and the person you like.

24:39.820 --> 24:40.699
Why?

24:43.619 --> 24:45.580
Why do you like her so much?

24:45.699 --> 24:47.419
What's so great about Ruan Yu?

24:48.659 --> 24:49.139
Do you know

24:49.139 --> 24:50.500
how she treats me?

24:50.980 --> 24:52.659
Do you think she's a good person?

24:52.859 --> 24:53.580
Ruan Yu didn't do anything

24:53.580 --> 24:54.580
wrong to you.

24:55.459 --> 24:57.540
You made a mistake.

24:58.260 --> 24:59.139
She wasn't treating you badly.

24:59.379 --> 25:00.379
She was just protecting herself

25:00.379 --> 25:01.060
to protect herself.

25:01.980 --> 25:02.899
And what about you?

25:03.419 --> 25:04.500
She doesn't reciprocate your feelings,

25:04.939 --> 25:06.580
yet she still holds onto you.

25:06.820 --> 25:07.980
Why does she get to

25:08.219 --> 25:09.300
have you all to herself?

25:13.780 --> 25:15.219
She doesn't even know I like her.

25:16.659 --> 25:17.619
How can she hold onto me?

25:18.980 --> 25:19.740
Over the years,

25:20.139 --> 25:21.340
the number of times I've seen her

25:21.859 --> 25:22.980
can be counted on one hand.

25:26.459 --> 25:28.459
But you still only see her.

25:29.139 --> 25:30.899
I knew you first.

25:31.580 --> 25:32.619
I've tried so hard

25:32.619 --> 25:33.859
to be like her.

25:35.899 --> 25:36.980
But why can't you

25:36.980 --> 25:38.379
see my pain?

25:39.619 --> 25:40.139
It's because

25:40.139 --> 25:41.100
I see your pain

25:41.260 --> 25:42.580
that I want you to let go of yourself.

25:42.980 --> 25:43.820
You're already good enough.

25:44.500 --> 25:45.619
You don't need to change for anyone,

25:46.419 --> 25:47.659
or imitate anyone.

25:51.659 --> 25:52.219
Then,

25:52.899 --> 25:54.179
will you like me?

25:56.379 --> 25:57.179
Even if it's not me,

25:58.419 --> 25:59.260
you will meet someone

26:00.020 --> 26:00.740
who likes you.

26:01.020 --> 26:02.260
I don't want anyone else.

26:10.260 --> 26:11.020
I'm sorry.

26:16.859 --> 26:17.980
I'm begging you.

26:21.300 --> 26:21.980
Can you...

26:22.699 --> 26:23.300
Can you

26:23.300 --> 26:24.580
stop liking Ruan Yu?

26:26.300 --> 26:27.939
Can you stop working?

26:28.340 --> 26:29.699
Can you stop singing?

26:30.619 --> 26:31.419
Can you spend more time with me

26:31.419 --> 26:32.419
like this?

26:34.459 --> 26:35.300
Can you?

26:39.780 --> 26:41.659
What if I say no?

26:48.379 --> 26:49.340
Then I don't know

26:49.340 --> 26:50.619
what I would do

26:53.899 --> 26:54.859
to myself

26:56.699 --> 26:57.899
and to Ruan Yu.

26:59.740 --> 27:00.619
Have you ever thought

27:00.859 --> 27:02.340
that you don't like me at all?

27:02.580 --> 27:03.459
Then what is it?

27:05.060 --> 27:06.820
I just want to be with you.

27:07.340 --> 27:09.139
I can die for you.

27:09.340 --> 27:10.699
Isn't that love?

27:12.179 --> 27:13.060
At least,

27:13.939 --> 27:14.980
I don't think love

27:15.540 --> 27:16.859
means moral coercion,

27:18.179 --> 27:19.500
or threatening someone

27:20.300 --> 27:21.020
with the people they care about.

27:25.179 --> 27:26.379
Do you hate me now?

27:31.459 --> 27:32.100
It's not hate.

27:33.859 --> 27:34.500
It's disappointment.

27:35.740 --> 27:36.980
I treated you kindly

27:37.780 --> 27:38.899
because I saw you as a friend.

27:39.820 --> 27:40.820
That's not love.

27:41.580 --> 27:42.939
It doesn't mean our lives

27:42.939 --> 27:43.780
are tied together.

27:46.459 --> 27:47.699
Your possessiveness

27:48.060 --> 27:48.899
and control issues

27:51.139 --> 27:52.179
are just symptoms of your illness.

27:54.219 --> 27:54.980
Get well soon.

27:56.820 --> 27:57.459
Don't...

28:05.340 --> 28:06.419
Betting your life

28:07.659 --> 28:08.219
will only hurt

28:08.219 --> 28:09.179
your family who loves you.

28:10.219 --> 28:11.100
As for Ruan Yu,

28:12.899 --> 28:13.899
If it weren't for you,

28:15.260 --> 28:16.340
I wouldn't have had the chance to find her.

28:16.740 --> 28:17.820
No, no.

28:17.820 --> 28:18.419
If you still want

28:18.419 --> 28:19.260
to do something,

28:20.899 --> 28:22.100
I will do whatever it takes.

28:22.300 --> 28:23.580
No, I won't do it anymore.

28:24.659 --> 28:25.459
I won't do it anymore.

28:25.659 --> 28:26.659
Don't go looking for her.

28:27.060 --> 28:28.580
Don't go looking for her.

28:41.260 --> 28:41.939
I didn't expect

28:41.939 --> 28:43.459
Lawyer Xu to have such exquisite knife skills.

28:44.060 --> 28:44.859
I thought

28:45.060 --> 28:46.260
hands like yours

28:46.340 --> 28:47.260
would rarely touch a cutting board.

28:48.899 --> 28:49.459
Precious?

28:51.419 --> 28:52.419
Don't people say

28:52.580 --> 28:53.419
that piano players

28:53.419 --> 28:54.459
insure their hands?

28:55.300 --> 28:56.899
That I play the piano

28:58.300 --> 28:59.340
is another online rumor.

29:01.899 --> 29:02.419
Yeah.

29:02.859 --> 29:03.859
The reports say

29:03.980 --> 29:05.939
you're quite skilled at the piano

29:06.219 --> 29:07.980
and has a deep understanding of music.

29:10.100 --> 29:10.859
I thought

29:10.859 --> 29:12.260
you saw that piano.

29:19.340 --> 29:20.300
I shouldn't have said that.

29:27.139 --> 29:28.100
What's wrong, Lawyer Xu?

29:29.659 --> 29:30.179
Nothing.

29:31.020 --> 29:31.699
The smoke alarm system

29:31.699 --> 29:33.139
of this apartment is quite sensitive.

29:33.340 --> 29:34.500
There was a false alarm before,

29:34.780 --> 29:36.020
which caused the whole building to sound the alarm.

29:36.300 --> 29:37.060
It's quite troublesome.

29:46.899 --> 29:48.100
Did you often cook for yourself

29:48.300 --> 29:50.020
when you were in the US?

29:50.300 --> 29:51.260
Not really.

29:51.659 --> 29:52.500
Cooking is a way

29:52.500 --> 29:53.780
to relieve stress for me.

29:54.939 --> 29:56.540
Cutting, frying,

29:56.740 --> 29:58.100
stirring, and serving.

29:59.340 --> 30:01.379
The process is fixed,

30:02.020 --> 30:03.419
just like a lawsuit.

30:04.340 --> 30:05.659
But different heat

30:05.899 --> 30:06.740
and seasonings

30:06.899 --> 30:08.340
create different flavors.

30:08.820 --> 30:09.459
It's like

30:09.459 --> 30:10.780
the process of a lawsuit,

30:11.179 --> 30:11.859
there will be surprises

30:12.260 --> 30:13.139
and shocks.

30:14.699 --> 30:15.820
What if it's a shock?

30:16.619 --> 30:17.500
What should we do?

30:20.419 --> 30:21.459
If it can be controlled,

30:21.899 --> 30:22.939
try not to

30:23.219 --> 30:24.540
repeat the same mistakes.

30:26.219 --> 30:27.580
If it can't be controlled,

30:28.100 --> 30:29.020
just get rid of it.

30:30.419 --> 30:31.300
Don't blame yourself

30:31.699 --> 30:33.020
for the mistakes of others.

30:38.260 --> 30:38.899
Lawyer Xu,

30:40.020 --> 30:41.379
this is the first time I've heard you

30:42.020 --> 30:42.659
speak this much

30:42.659 --> 30:43.659
aside from analyzing cases.

30:44.300 --> 30:46.139
Is it strange?

30:47.060 --> 30:47.659
Not at all.

30:49.060 --> 30:50.060
It's a pleasant surprise,

30:50.699 --> 30:51.500
not a shock.

31:02.260 --> 31:03.859
Ruan Yu, are you a traitor?

31:03.859 --> 31:04.820
You hung up on me?

31:05.060 --> 31:05.980
What did Lawyer Xu

31:05.980 --> 31:07.619
feed you to make you so loyal?

31:12.300 --> 31:13.260
Lawyer Xu,

31:13.260 --> 31:14.619
is there anything

31:14.619 --> 31:15.659
I can help with?

31:15.939 --> 31:16.419
It's okay.

31:16.699 --> 31:17.899
You go rest in the living room.

31:18.219 --> 31:20.500
I'm going to make some soup.

31:22.419 --> 31:23.939
Okay, thanks.

31:33.260 --> 31:35.139
Why do you like her so much?

31:35.379 --> 31:36.980
What's so good about Ruan Yu?

31:48.419 --> 31:49.379
You saw it with your own eyes

31:49.379 --> 31:50.179
when I tried it.

31:50.899 --> 31:51.659
I didn't drop it.

31:52.179 --> 31:53.899
How could it suddenly crack?

31:54.219 --> 31:55.139
Are you kidding?

31:55.740 --> 31:56.820
It was already cracked.

31:57.020 --> 31:58.100
Do you have any proof?

32:02.260 --> 32:03.219
Isn't there a camera?

32:04.939 --> 32:05.699
It's broken.

32:07.939 --> 32:08.500
Then...

32:09.859 --> 32:11.500
what do you want me to do?

32:11.820 --> 32:12.939
I'll cut you some slack

32:13.379 --> 32:15.179
since you're a student.

32:15.820 --> 32:17.139
Just pay me 3,000 yuan.

32:17.659 --> 32:18.619
3,000 yuan?

32:21.060 --> 32:22.139
My monthly living expenses

32:22.139 --> 32:22.980
are just over 1,000.

32:23.060 --> 32:23.820
I don't care.

32:24.219 --> 32:25.419
If you don't want to pay,

32:25.419 --> 32:26.179
I'll call the police.

32:27.260 --> 32:27.899
Don't, I...

32:27.899 --> 32:28.780
Then call the police.

32:46.899 --> 32:48.260
She's right.

32:48.379 --> 32:49.699
If you don't pay, we'll call the police.

32:50.740 --> 32:51.859
This second-hand guitar

32:52.020 --> 32:52.780
must be from your store,

32:52.780 --> 32:53.699
right?

32:54.179 --> 32:54.980
With this cracked guitar,

32:54.980 --> 32:55.980
how many people have you cheated

32:55.980 --> 32:56.780
for a long time?

32:57.459 --> 32:58.340
3,000 yuan

32:59.100 --> 33:00.580
is enough to constitute the crime of fraud.

33:00.820 --> 33:01.859
You should call the police.

33:02.459 --> 33:03.859
I don't understand what you said.

33:04.300 --> 33:05.139
It's okay if you don't understand.

33:06.060 --> 33:07.139
Then let the uncle policeman

33:07.139 --> 33:08.179
translate for you.

33:09.740 --> 33:10.859
If you don't want to buy it, forget it.

33:10.859 --> 33:11.540
Don't make trouble here.

33:11.780 --> 33:12.500
Go away.

33:19.459 --> 33:20.060
Thank you.

33:21.060 --> 33:21.699
It's nothing.

33:22.379 --> 33:23.260
Do you want to buy a guitar?

33:25.740 --> 33:26.260
No.

33:26.859 --> 33:28.300
I just have a look.

33:34.060 --> 33:34.659
Shi Can

33:35.859 --> 33:36.580
Happy birthday.

33:37.699 --> 33:38.459
May you become

33:38.580 --> 33:39.939
the person you want to be.

33:43.179 --> 33:45.340
How do you know my birthday?

33:45.980 --> 33:47.300
It's on your interview materials.

33:47.939 --> 33:49.179
But it's too expensive.

33:49.540 --> 33:50.139
I can't take it.

33:51.939 --> 33:52.780
We all chip in

33:52.780 --> 33:53.580
to buy it.

33:53.740 --> 33:54.740
It's not expensive.

33:55.419 --> 33:56.379
Yeah, just take it.

33:56.379 --> 33:57.619
Take it.

33:58.740 --> 33:59.379
I can't.

33:59.740 --> 34:01.100
Just take it.

34:01.419 --> 34:02.699
Our male lead

34:02.699 --> 34:03.500
should have a

34:03.500 --> 34:04.580
beautiful guitar.

34:05.419 --> 34:05.980
Besides,

34:06.459 --> 34:07.820
it's engraved with words. You can't return it.

34:08.139 --> 34:09.500
Yeah, Ruan Yu

34:09.980 --> 34:11.459
spent a long time on the engraving.

34:12.139 --> 34:12.980
Open it and see.

34:13.659 --> 34:14.060
Open it.

34:14.060 --> 34:14.820
Open it.

34:14.899 --> 34:15.379
Open it.

34:16.259 --> 34:16.819
Okay.

34:33.659 --> 34:36.460
The road ahead is long and bright.

34:43.060 --> 34:43.500
Bro,

34:44.659 --> 34:45.219
are you okay?

34:46.020 --> 34:47.699
I've been watching you for a while.

34:51.900 --> 34:52.380
Bro,

34:53.219 --> 34:54.580
are you still worrying about

34:54.580 --> 34:55.619
Cen Sisi?

34:56.339 --> 34:57.219
In my opinion,

34:57.339 --> 34:59.380
someone who hinders you from pursuing

34:59.380 --> 35:00.139
your dream and career,

35:00.139 --> 35:01.619
you don't need to care about her.

35:04.819 --> 35:05.860
I'm thinking about

35:06.980 --> 35:08.179
the first person who supports my dream.

35:09.860 --> 35:10.380
Who is she?

35:15.100 --> 35:15.580
Xiao Fei,

35:16.139 --> 35:17.699
Do you have a girl you like?

35:18.060 --> 35:18.860
Yeah.

35:20.460 --> 35:21.699
The supporting actress

35:22.339 --> 35:23.179
in the TV series

35:23.179 --> 35:24.020
last month.

35:24.819 --> 35:25.940
I mean if...

35:26.540 --> 35:27.259
If

35:28.139 --> 35:29.339
the person you like

35:29.659 --> 35:31.259
has someone she likes for a long time.

35:31.779 --> 35:33.500
After being apart for many years,

35:33.659 --> 35:34.659
they meet again.

35:34.900 --> 35:38.100
You want to support her happiness,

35:38.980 --> 35:39.980
so you chose

35:39.980 --> 35:41.980
to hide your feelings.

35:42.860 --> 35:43.940
But after a while,

35:44.460 --> 35:45.179
you found that

35:45.179 --> 35:46.699
they were just friends.

35:47.580 --> 35:49.259
Maybe she

35:49.659 --> 35:51.179
doesn't like him anymore.

35:51.779 --> 35:52.259
Then,

35:53.819 --> 35:54.500
what would you do?

35:54.739 --> 35:55.860
Of course, I'll go for it.

35:57.779 --> 35:58.819
But if you fail,

35:59.139 --> 35:59.940
you can't even be

35:59.940 --> 36:00.500
lose her as a friend?

36:00.900 --> 36:03.299
Take the plunge, and you might get more than you expect.

36:04.699 --> 36:06.380
If it fails, just start over.

36:11.940 --> 36:12.339
Bro,

36:12.900 --> 36:13.900
why are you asking me this?

36:16.060 --> 36:16.739
Just curious.

36:19.580 --> 36:21.219
Bro, you don't have

36:21.219 --> 36:22.500
a girl you like, do you?

36:26.619 --> 36:27.380
Can't I?

36:37.659 --> 36:39.259
How are you doing with Lawyer Xu?

36:39.659 --> 36:41.299
If it's uncomfortable, just tell me.

36:41.659 --> 36:42.339
I'll come pick you up.

36:45.259 --> 36:45.779
I'll do it.

36:46.819 --> 36:47.420
Could you please

36:47.420 --> 36:48.299
help me with the dishes?

36:48.659 --> 36:49.139
Thank you.

36:55.659 --> 36:56.619
And the soup spoon.

37:21.500 --> 37:22.739
[You haven't replied for so long.]

37:24.100 --> 37:25.100
[What are you doing?]

38:01.779 --> 38:03.500
[I forgot to bring the hair tie in a hurry.]

38:11.259 --> 38:12.139
Would you like some more?

38:16.540 --> 38:18.219
[Ruan Yu, are you a womanizer?]

38:18.219 --> 38:19.139
[What did Lawyer Xu]

38:19.139 --> 38:20.980
[put in your head?]

38:23.940 --> 38:24.339
Come on.

38:24.779 --> 38:25.420
Enough.

38:27.619 --> 38:28.100
Okay.

38:33.659 --> 38:34.380
Well,

38:37.299 --> 38:39.100
I've changed the sheets,

38:39.100 --> 38:40.339
duvet cover and pillowcases.

38:41.540 --> 38:42.500
You can go to the bedroom

38:42.980 --> 38:44.139
and see if there's anything missing.

38:44.699 --> 38:45.179
Okay.

39:02.619 --> 39:03.179
[No way.]

39:03.659 --> 39:04.380
[With everything]

39:04.380 --> 39:04.980
[that's happened today,]

39:05.739 --> 39:06.900
If he takes advantage of me,

39:07.540 --> 39:08.580
he's a scum.

39:15.380 --> 39:16.460
What if he is a scum?

39:40.420 --> 39:41.900
Hello, seniors.

39:42.420 --> 39:44.420
I'm Li Shican, a freshman.

39:44.940 --> 39:45.940
I'm here for an interview

39:45.940 --> 39:46.940
to join the Arts Department.

39:47.580 --> 39:48.900
I'm going to

39:48.900 --> 39:49.779
sing a song

39:49.779 --> 39:51.739
I composed.

39:52.380 --> 39:53.020
Endless.

40:05.020 --> 40:05.659
Take it easy.

40:07.460 --> 40:09.259
Just pretend we're all your fans

40:09.460 --> 40:10.540
here to see you perform.

41:16.940 --> 41:18.380
What kind of lousy weather is this?

41:18.619 --> 41:19.779
It's raining so hard.

41:20.980 --> 41:22.219
Why hasn't my mom come yet?

41:50.500 --> 41:51.500
[Did he forget his umbrella?]

41:53.380 --> 41:55.139
[If I offer to share my umbrella with him,]

41:55.540 --> 41:57.100
[wouldn't that be weird?]

41:58.100 --> 41:59.179
[After all, in his eyes,]

41:59.779 --> 42:00.819
[we don't know each other at all.]

42:16.339 --> 42:16.860
Ruan Yu,

42:17.420 --> 42:18.299
you forgot your umbrella.

42:18.619 --> 42:19.619
Do you want to share an umbrella with me?

42:20.380 --> 42:20.860
No, thanks.

42:21.139 --> 42:22.460
I need to go somewhere else.

42:22.619 --> 42:23.420
And the rain

42:23.500 --> 42:24.540
will probably stop in a while.

42:24.860 --> 42:25.580
You go first.

42:26.139 --> 42:26.980
Then I'll go first, Ruan Yu.

42:27.299 --> 42:27.659
Bye.

42:27.860 --> 42:28.259
Bye.

42:34.179 --> 42:35.060
What a nice day.

42:35.060 --> 42:35.940
It's really a nice day.

42:36.420 --> 42:36.940
Rain,

42:37.299 --> 42:38.460
please keep falling

42:38.619 --> 42:39.500
for a little longer.

43:35.500 --> 43:35.980
My girl.

43:36.420 --> 43:37.420
Mom.

43:37.699 --> 43:38.540
[Dear heavens,]

43:38.779 --> 43:39.739
[I've been hoping for my mom]

43:39.739 --> 43:40.219
[to come back]

43:40.219 --> 43:41.500
[for ten minutes now.]

43:41.619 --> 43:43.179
[I can't keep holding out hope.]

43:43.420 --> 43:43.900
My girl,

43:44.580 --> 43:45.259
sorry I'm late.

43:45.819 --> 43:46.580
It's okay.

43:47.100 --> 43:48.299
I didn't see you at the bus stop.

43:48.699 --> 43:49.900
I knew you were stuck at school.

43:50.380 --> 43:50.779
Let's go.

43:52.380 --> 43:53.179
Isn't this Xu Huaisong?

43:53.779 --> 43:54.339
What's up, Teacher Qu?

43:54.339 --> 43:55.179
You don't have an umbrella either.

43:56.940 --> 43:58.339
Why don't you come with me?

43:58.860 --> 43:59.580
The umbrella is a bit small,

43:59.580 --> 44:00.179
but the three of us can squeeze in.

44:00.179 --> 44:00.739
Is that okay?

44:02.900 --> 44:03.659
No need, teacher.

44:03.819 --> 44:04.380
I'm waiting for someone.

44:04.619 --> 44:05.699
Someone's coming to pick you up?

44:06.219 --> 44:07.179
Alright, let's go then.

44:08.500 --> 44:09.020
Come on.

44:09.619 --> 44:10.020
You,

44:10.020 --> 44:11.339
pay more attention to that essay.

44:11.339 --> 44:11.940
Got it?

44:12.020 --> 44:12.420
Let's go.

44:12.420 --> 44:12.980
Goodbye, teacher.
